item.title: CVE-2017-2868|2024-09-16T19:01:11.369Z -- natus%20medical%20incorporated -- natus
item.description: An exploitable code execution vulnerability exists in the NewProducerStream functionality of Natus Xltek NeuroWorks 8. A specially crafted network packet can cause a stack buffer overflow resulting in code execution. An attacker can send a malicious packet to trigger this vulnerability.
